edu.cmu.tetrad.search

Class IndTestMimBuild

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.tetrad.search.IndTestMimBuild
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndependenceTest
    Deprecated.

    public final class IndTestMimBuild
extends Object
implements IndependenceTest
    Checks the independence of latent variables in a measurement model by constructing estimating its parameters under the special conditions illustrated by Figure 12.18 of CPS, 2nd edition. This is basically a test of the rank of the covariance matrix of latents.
    Author:
    Ricardo Silva
